data.description: This charming 3 bedroom/1.5 bath home is located in Coraopolis Boro - close to the airport and I79.   There have been several updates in the past year including a new hot water boiler and an updated full bathroom. This home boasts a large covered front porch, a great yard and  off street parking in the back of the home. The den on the 1st floor could be an additional bedroom.
